Package org.planit.output.configuration

Class LinkOutputTypeConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.planit.output.configuration.OutputTypeConfiguration
      • org.planit.output.configuration.LinkOutputTypeConfiguration
  • public class LinkOutputTypeConfiguration
extends OutputTypeConfiguration
    The configuration for the link output type. The following OutputProperty values are included by default:
    • MODE_ID
    • MODE_XML_ID
    • FLOW CAPACITY_PER_LANE
    • NUMBER_OF_LANES LENGTH
    • CALCULATED_SPEED COST
    • DENSITY LINK_SEGMENT_ID
    • UPSTREAM_NODE_ID
    • UPSTREAM_NODE_XML_ID
    • UPSTREAM_NODE_LOCATION
    • DOWNSTREAM_NODE_ID
    • DOWNSTREAM_NODE_XML_ID
    • DOWNSTREAM_NODE_LOCATION
    • CAPACITY_PER_LANE
    • LINK_COST
    • MAXIMUM_SPEED
    • TIME_PERIOD_XML_ID
    • TIME_PERIOD_ID
    Author:
    markr
